1. Install all dependencies like npm, truffle, ganache
2. Download metamask extension.
3. Choose a suitable IDE to compile your solidity code on
4. Install Ganache and have a local blockchain running.
5. Install truffle and rpc and navigate to the directory and code: truffle init
6. Configure truffle to interact with Ganache
7. Launch truffle console and fetch data from 10 free ether accounts in Ganache
4. Perform a smoke test.
